data.description: A beautiful  raised ranch sitting in the quiet subdivision of Pell Lake is waiting for you! 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms, featuring an open concept kitchen/living room with vaulted ceilings and ample cabinet space. Walk out from the kitchen onto a raised deck, overviewing a new fenced in yard.  Lower level offers a rec room and family room with a 2 car attached garage.  Newer GE washer and dryer. Security system, gas furnace, electric water heater and forced air ac.  Schedule a showing before it goes!
